        "name": "SQA Gradation 4 — formal version control, regression suite, and documented release procedure",
        "description": "The CFD solver must be maintained under a formal version-control system (Git with tagged releases), a regression test suite covering at least 20 canonical flow cases must pass before each release, and a documented release procedure including change-log review must be followed. Achieved: OpenFOAM v9 with institutional fork under GitLab CI/CD; 34 regression cases pass; release notes reviewed by two independent engineers."
      },
      "rationale": "At MRL 5 the solver underpins a primary regulatory submission for a Class III device. Formal SQA at Gradation 4 is required and has been demonstrated through institutional GitLab CI/CD pipeline, 34-case regression suite, and dual-engineer release review."
