        "description": "All experimental boundary conditions (inlet flow rate ± 0.5%, rotational speed ± 0.1 RPM, fluid viscosity and density ± 1%) must be documented and replicated in the simulation. Achieved: FDA benchmark protocol followed; inlet flow rates and impeller speeds documented in lab notebook LN-2024-07; fluid properties measured at test temperature and applied directly as CFD boundary conditions."
