        "description": "Predicted NIH must agree with experimental NIH within combined simulation and experimental uncertainty (95% CI) at all 5 operating points; agreement metric E_rms < 15%. Achieved: E_rms = 11.3% across all operating points; experimental and simulation 95% CI bands overlap at all points; detailed in validation report VR-2025-05."
