        "description": "The simulation QoI (Normalised Index of Hemolysis, NIH) must be the same quantity used in clinical and regulatory hemolysis thresholds; a documented traceability chain from NIH to the ISO 10993-4 haemocompatibility endpoint must be provided. Achieved: NIH traceability documented in design dossier DD-2025-02, referencing ISO 10993-4 and FDA guidance on blood-contacting devices."
