        "description": "Residuals must converge to at least 10^-6 for all transport equations; round-off error assessed via double-precision arithmetic confirmation; iterative error contribution to NIH must be < 0.5%. Achieved: All residuals reach 10^-7; double-precision confirmed; iterative error in NIH estimated at 0.08% via Richardson extrapolation on iteration count."
